title: Microsoft Azure Firewall: Latency
agents: azure_v2
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the latency of Microsoft Azure Firewalls.

 The service displays the latency in milliseconds and allows you to
 configure upper warning and critical thresholds.

 You can configure the warning and critical levels using the rule
 "Azure Firewall Latency".

 In order to use this check, you need to configure the Azure special agent.

discovery:
 One service is created for each Azure Firewall.
